Native Instruments Solid EQ v1.1.1 Update







The SOLID EQ is a precise 6-band workhorse equalizer ready for anything from subtle shading to aggressive shaping.

Available separately or as a part of the SOLID MIX SERIES bundle, SOLID EQ delivers instant, transparent results and boasts a clean new interface for dialing up professional sound with total ease.
